txt.en: 'The West Gate is fully rebuilt and ready to be manned. It is a dangerous post, looking out into the hills of the East Wall, and one we will want well-guarded, for it is surely where the Enemy will march from. Brave warriors will be needed to stand guard.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
Bring the Tokens of Hytbold to Harsterre
